### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Register New Player
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "pamela_test",
  "email": "pamela@test.com",
  "password": "senha123",
  "confirmPassword": "senha123"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "pamela_test",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Extract Token
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Get All Towers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/towers

### Get Towers by Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/towers/type/Physical

### Update Score (Requires Auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/score/update
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 1500
}

### Get Current Score
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/score/current
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Top 10 Leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard/top10

### Get Top 50 Leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard/top/50

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
